    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>using pattern template method to execute common tasks before and later action without intercepting filter</p>

<p>class Zend_Controller_Action
{
protected function _beforeAction() { }
protected function _laterAction() { }</p>

<p>public unction run(...,...)
{
...
$this-&gt;_beforeAction();
$this-&gt;$method();
$this-&gt;_laterAction();
...
}
}</p>

